https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7Sr167mY8d84dQekq8TJlPOIVrB.jpg Bill Coors is known for being a titan of the brewing industry but what is less known is the heroic personal journey he undertook to discover a holistic answer to treat the depression and anxiety that had plagued his family for generations. Bill's journey is told parallel to several young internet influencers - although 100 years divides them - their stories are eerily similar as is their fierce 'Will to Live." Bill Coors: The Will to Live
